fects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/158921/', '', 'Ketotifen, Tetracaine', 'Methotrimeprazine, Promazine, Pimavanserin, Amisulpride, Triflupromazine', 1767369485);
